Package io.emkode

Class SievePrimeGenerator

java.lang.Object
io.emkode.SievePrimeGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrimeNumberGenerator
public class SievePrimeGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrimeNumberGenerator
An implementation of PrimeNumberGenerator, using the Sieve of Eratosthenes. Generates prime numbers within a range, or returns the prime-ness of a single value.
